#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:321
msgid "机器人负载曲线"
msgstr "Robot Load Curve"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:324
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:325
msgid "负载曲线用于描述机器人的负载能力，可协助用户进行型号选择，并评估所安装末端负载的可行性。"
msgstr ""
"The load curve describes the robot’s load capacity, helping users select "
"appropriate models and assess the feasibility of the installed end-effector "
"load."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:328
msgid "负载曲线"
msgstr "Load curve"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:329
msgid ""
"本节所涉及的负载曲线基于ART3-R7在不同全局运行速度(30%、50%，80%和100%)，执行特定轨迹仿真获取。负载曲线存在“完整性能”和“扩展后的负载能力”两部分，具体如下："
msgstr ""
"The load curves covered in this section are obtained from trajectory "
"simulations of the ART3-R7 robot at different global operating speeds (30%, "
"50%, 80%, and 100%). Each load curve consists of two parts: “Full "
"Performance” and “Extended Load Capacity,” as detailed below:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:331
msgid ""
"“完整性能”的运行环境为：各关节摩擦力补偿系数为1；各关节碰撞等级为10；Web界面设置相应运行速度，维护模式内加速度默认为360deg/s\\ "
":sup:`2` ；动力学2.0。在此环境下，负载曲线“完整性能”部分适应绝大多数运行轨迹。"
msgstr ""
"The “Full Performance” operating environment is defined as follows: friction"
" compensation coefficients for all joints are set to 1; collision "
"sensitivity levels for all joints are set to 10; the corresponding operating"
" speed is configured via the Web interface; the default acceleration in "
"Maintenance Mode is 360 deg/s²; and Dynamics 2.0 is enabled. Under this "
"environment, the “Full Performance” segment of the payload curve "
"accommodates the vast majority of motion trajectories."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:332
msgid "若末端负载处于“扩展后的负载能力”，须开启“时间最优模式”并满足加速度限制，或减小机器人工作范围。"
msgstr ""
"If the end-effector load is within the “extended load capacity,” the “time-"
"optimal mode” must be enabled while satisfying the acceleration limits, or "
"the robot’s working range must be reduced."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:335
msgid "参数说明"
msgstr "Parameter Description"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:336
msgid "机器人的额定有效负载取决于有效负载的重心偏移，其中，重心偏移定义为末端法兰中心与附加的有效负载重心之间的距离。"
msgstr ""
"The robot’s rated payload depends on the center-of-gravity offset of the "
"payload, defined as the distance between the center of the end flange and "
"the center of gravity of the attached payload."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:339
msgid "30%运行速度下的负载曲线"
msgstr "Load curve at 30% operating speed"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:341
msgid "在30%全局运行速度下，ART3-R7型号机器人最大可携带负载为5kg，额定负载为3kg，负载曲线下图所示。负载曲线的具体释义如下："
msgstr ""
"At 30% of the global operating speed, the ART3-R7 robot model has a maximum "
"payload capacity of 5 kg and a rated payload of 3 kg, as shown in the "
"payload curve below. The payload curve is interpreted as follows:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:343
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:361
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:379
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:397
msgid "ART3-R7在完整性能下可携带3kg及以下的负载，见“蓝色包络线”；"
msgstr ""
"ART3-R7 can carry a load of 3 kg or less at full performance, as shown by "
"the “blue envelope.”"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:344
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:362
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:380
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:398
msgid "当负载为3kg至5kg时，为扩展后的负载能力，见“红色包络线”，此时机器人可运行在如下状态："
msgstr ""
"When the load is 3 kg to 5 kg, the extended load capacity (see the “red "
"envelope curve”) allows the robot to operate in the following states:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:346
msgid "①开启“时间最优模式”，建议加速度设置在108deg/s\\ :sup:`2` 以下；"
msgstr ""
"① Enable “Time-Optimal Mode”; it is recommended to set the acceleration "
"below 108 deg/s²."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:348
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:366
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:384
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:402
msgid "②减小机器人工作范围，避免频繁冲击。"
msgstr "② Reduce the robot’s working range to avoid frequent impacts."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:-1
msgid "048.png"
msgstr "048.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:355
msgid "图表 3-19 负载曲线—全局运行速度30%"
msgstr "Figure 3-19 Load Curve—Global Operating Speed at 30%"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_product.rst:357
msgid "50%运行速度下的负载曲线"
